707097f.title: Brooklyn: Ave. U - 13th St. E.
707097f.text:
Ave. U. at the N.E. corner of East 13th Street. The buildings
facing AVe. U, were razed to make way for 3-story business and residential
brick buildings.
About 1906.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
